{"inkVersion":21,"root":[[{"->":"chapter_4"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"chapter_4":["^$DISABLE_ALL_ACTIONS ","#","^auto:true","/#","\n","^$SLEEP:1 ","#","^auto:true","/#","\n","^“……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_sad_1 ","/#","#","^avatar_opacity:0.01","/#","\n","^“…………” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_sad_1 ","/#","#","^avatar_opacity:0.1","/#","\n","^“……磷光……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_sad_2 ","/#","#","^avatar_opacity:1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la","/#","\n","^“你在哭？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_0.5 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“呜啊！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_scared ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_mi","/#","\n","^“我才没在哭！你，你什么时候！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“不对，你真的是磷光？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_thinking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“还能有假？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“你知道我是谁？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_seriously_thinking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“你不是薄明？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_0.5 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“我确实是薄明来着……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_spaceout ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“为什么是这么不确定的语气。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_happy_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“不对！不要转移话题！为什么刚刚突然就没信号了！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_angry_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“哪里转移话题了……明明我们根本没聊到这个问题上。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_awkward ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“我快担心死了……上一秒还在说话，突然间就什么都看不到了，耳边只有无线电的背景噪音……航标灯也灭了！到底发生什么了！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“对不起，是发电机停机了。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“停机？没油了？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“是。我本来以为还能坚持半天。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_awkward ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“可是发电机不是在地下室……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_confused ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la","/#","\n","^“啊，我的万能钥匙派上用场了？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“嗯，多亏了它。谢谢。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“嘿嘿，不客气。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_3 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“不过有另外一个坏消息，灯塔里只剩最后一箱柴油了。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“虽然说理论上补给应该早在前两天就到了——备用钥匙也是——但大概是因为天气原因一直没来。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_look_upwards ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“那，现在的油量还能撑多久？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_confused ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“如果保持航标灯常亮……保守估计，十二个小时吧。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_thinking_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“那如果关掉航标灯呢？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_thinking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“应该能撑过一天？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_0.5 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“这样吗……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_seriously_thinking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la","/#","\n","^“但毕竟不可能关掉啊。在夜间和能见度低下的时候开启航标灯，这是作为灯塔最基本的要求。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“没关系！把航标灯关掉吧！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“都说了不能关的啦……” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_awkward ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“我来代替灯塔。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“欸？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_flip_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“「薄明号」有桅灯！这可以代替航标灯吧？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“……很遗憾，不能。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“欸——为什么？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“能见距离不够。你知道菲涅尔透镜吗？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“好像对这个名字有点印象。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“简单来说就是一种光学装置，安装在光源外，能让很远的地方也能看到航标灯。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“「磷光」的能见范围是 15 海里。一般的桅灯，最多只有 5 海里吧？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_look_upwards ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“那把菲涅尔透镜拆下来……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“拆不下来。它有快三米高。就算拆下来了也装不到桅杆上去。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_happy_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“那看来只能给桅灯升压了。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_seriously_thinking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“……你最好别。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_awkward ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“好啦我知道你是在为我考虑。但不管怎么说撑过这个晚上还是足够的。就祈祷明天他们会把补给送到吧。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“‘他们’是谁？海岸警卫队吗？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“不是，是最近的小镇的人。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_happy_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“「磷光」是离岸灯塔，离小镇大概有 12 千米远。平时燃油和食物都是从那里补给的。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“以及，那里也是我的故乡。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“欸，是这样吗！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_4 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_mi","/#","\n","^“那是个……什么样的地方？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“单调，冷清，小得可怜。海鸟比人多一万倍。走两个小时就能逛完。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_happy_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“呜啊，那是真的很小诶。你一直在那里长大的？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_3 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“是啊，很遗憾。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“很遗憾？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“毕竟我的故乡并不是什么值得一提的地方。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“没有的事喔。我觉得很浪漫啊。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“浪漫？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_0.5 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“是啊。明明是这么小的一个小镇，但对你来说就是整个世界吧？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“……是吧，是啊。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_default ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“小时候的我确实是这么觉得的。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“我的故乡，这个小镇，其实也是个‘离岸灯塔’。它建在一个小岛上，四面环海，距离我的国家的本土有四十千米。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“直到十四岁那年，父亲才第一次带我出岛。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_look_upwards ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“很兴奋？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“是啊，很兴奋，就像大航海时代发现新大陆的开拓者。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“是出去旅游？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“很遗憾，并不是。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“带我出岛，是为了将我登记为「磷光」的守塔人。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_happy_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“咦？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_mi","/#","\n","^“灯塔毕竟是统一由政府管理的。需要我本人到管理机构登记。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“不不不，十四岁就可以当守塔人了吗？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“就专业知识而言我可不比任何人差喔？我可是从小就开始和父亲学习灯塔维护的知识了。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confident_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“我倒不担心这个啦……十四岁不会太小了吗？还没有成年啊？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_thinking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“大概是因为没人愿意到这偏僻的地方值守吧，守塔人便只能代代相传。我父亲在把这个任务交给我之前，已经值守了三十年。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_thinking_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“那你父亲……” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_seriously_thinking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“在那之后的两个月后过世了，胃癌晚期。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_look_upwards ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“……我很抱歉。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_sad_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la","/#","\n","^“没事。我和他都很高兴灯塔依然能被我们好好留住。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“所以灯塔里一直只有你一个人？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“是的，我是现任唯一的守塔人。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confident_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“那你之后也会把这个灯塔传给你的孩子吗？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“不，我想我就是最后一任守塔人了吧。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“欸，为什么？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“灯塔已经过时了。现在的船舶都配备了卫星定位，现存的灯塔要么被废弃要么被自动化。由人管理维护的灯塔只会越来越少。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“「磷光」因为建在礁石群上，自动化改装成本高难度大，因此目前还是人工维护。”  ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_look_upwards ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“但我想……大概十年内就能见到它的结局了。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_sigh ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“好可惜啊。我还蛮喜欢灯塔给我的感觉的。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“什么感觉？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_flip_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“嗯……我不是说「薄明号」失去动力了？” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_ironic ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“是的？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_0.5 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“其实不完全。「薄明号」事实上触礁了。虽然控制住了进水，但失去了绝大部分置于储存仓的燃油。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“为了尽可能节约仅存的能源，我只保留了最低限度的用电设备。在光伏辅助下基本可以做到不耗油。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_la","/#","\n","^“在与你取得联系之前，我已经在大海上飘行了 155 个小时。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_ironic ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“155 个小时？连续 155 个小时没有救援？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_surprised ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“都说了啦，这是个自顾不暇的时代。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_released ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“其实并没有你想象中的这么严重。对我来说都是在茫茫的海面上飘罢了。只是为了省电几乎不开灯，这几天晚上又完全看不到月亮。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“夜晚的海……感觉一个不注意就会被黑暗吞没、无声无息地消失掉。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“那你还说可以代替灯塔，你这不是自己也没有能源了吗？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“嘿嘿，本来不想说的。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“这不是想不想说的问题吧……” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_awkward ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“不过……今天不是这样的。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“嗯？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_0.5 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“今天我看到了光。来自你的光。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“这可不是比喻喔。来自灯塔「磷光」的航标灯，是真的在无光的海面上穿过重重黑暗，向我奔来，就算是现在也是。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“我正看着你的光一遍又一遍扫过沉默的海面，我所在的「薄明号」，以及我。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“……” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_surprised","/#","\n","^“当然，这也是比喻。如果说此前 155 个小时的无线电静默是黑暗的大海，那来自你的无线电信号，就是那束刺破黑暗的航标灯光。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“所以如果要说灯塔给我的感觉，那一定是——” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“温暖。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_smile_1 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“……” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile","/#","\n","^“……谢谢，我很荣幸。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_happy_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“该说谢谢的是我。” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_3 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_do","/#","\n","^“啊！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_surprised_2 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_mi","/#","\n","^“怎么了？” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_confused_0.5 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_re","/#","\n","^“极光！你快来看！是极光！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_4 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_mi","/#","\n","^“是 2082 年的极光吧？我看不到的啦。” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_speaking ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","^“要试试看才知道嘛！快来灯笼房！” ","#","^type: LeftAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:薄明 ","/#","#","^avatar:holo_happy_3 ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_hakumei_re","/#","\n","^“好好……” ","#","^type:RightAvatarText ","/#","#","^speaker:磷光 ","/#","#","^avatar:phos_smile ","/#","#","^simulated_voice: sfx_phos_do","/#","\n","done",{"#f":1}],"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}